description: Create an Amazon CloudFront VPC origin.

parameters.name: VpcOriginEndpointConfig
parameters.description: The VPC origin endpoint configuration. The name of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. The ARN of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. The HTTP port for the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. The default value is 80. The HTTPS port of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. The default value is 443. The origin protocol policy for the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. OriginSslProtocols (dict) --- A complex type that contains information about the SSL/TLS protocols that CloudFront can use when establishing an HTTPS connection with your origin. The number of SSL/TLS protocols that you want to allow CloudFront to use when establishing an HTTPS connection with this origin. A list that contains allowed SSL/TLS protocols for this distribution. (string) ---

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration.

nested_params.name: Arn
nested_params.description: The ARN of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration.

nested_params.name: HTTPPort
nested_params.description: The HTTP port for the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. The default value is 80.

nested_params.name: HTTPSPort
nested_params.description: The HTTPS port of the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration. The default value is 443.

nested_params.name: OriginProtocolPolicy
nested_params.description: The origin protocol policy for the CloudFront VPC origin endpoint configuration.

nested_params.name: OriginSslProtocols
nested_params.description: A complex type that contains information about the SSL/TLS protocols that CloudFront can use when establishing an HTTPS connection with your origin.

nested_params.name: Quantity
nested_params.description: The number of SSL/TLS protocols that you want to allow CloudFront to use when establishing an HTTPS connection with this origin.

nested_params.name: Items
nested_params.description: A list that contains allowed SSL/TLS protocols for this distribution.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: A complex type that contains zero or more Tag elements. Items (list) --- A complex type that contains Tag elements. (dict) --- A complex type that contains Tag key and Tag value. A string that contains Tag key. The string length should be between 1 and 128 characters. Valid characters include a-z, A-Z, 0-9, space, and the special characters _ - . : / = + @. Value (string) --- A string that contains an optional Tag value. The string length should be between 0 and 256 characters. : / = + @.

nested_params.name: Items
nested_params.description: A complex type that contains Tag elements.

nested_params.name: Key
nested_params.description: A string that contains Tag key. The string length should be between 1 and 128 characters. Valid characters include a-z, A-Z, 0-9, space, and the special characters _ - . : / = + @.

nested_params.name: Value
nested_params.description: A string that contains an optional Tag value. The string length should be between 0 and 256 characters. Valid characters include a-z, A-Z, 0-9, space, and the special characters _ - . : / = + @.
